'''安德烈·諾蘭·道森'''（{{lang-en|Andre Nolan Dawson}}，{{bd|1954年|7月10日|}}），綽號「老鷹」和「傑出道森」，<ref>{{cite web  |url=http://archive.wtsp.com/sports/pro_baseball/rays/story.aspx?storyid%3D121856  |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140422001256/http://archive.wtsp.com/sports/pro_baseball/rays/story.aspx?storyid=121856  |archive-date=2014-04-22  |access-date=2014-04-22  |title=存档副本  |dead-url=yes  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20097276,00.html|title=No Series for the Cubbies, but at Least They Have Andre the Awesome|date=5 October 1987|website=people.com|access-date=2021-01-13|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822145739/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20097276,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goatriders.org/taxonomy/term/175 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100801092644/http://www.goatriders.org/taxonomy/term/175 |archive-date=2010-08-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手。21年職棒生涯分別效力於博覽會、小熊、紅襪與馬林魚等隊。

道森於1977年拿下國聯新人王，生涯入選8次明星賽。1987年，他拿下聯盟的全壘打王和打點王，並同時囊括金手套獎、銀棒獎與年度MVP。

道森原本是名中外野手，不過博覽會隊主場[[蒙特婁奧林匹克體育場|蒙特婁奧林匹克體育場]]的人工草皮讓他的膝蓋出現問題，使他被迫移防右外野。不過他生涯仍拿下8座金手套獎，最後他在2010年入選名人堂。<ref name="AP-HOF">{{cite web |last=Blum |first=Ronald |title=Andre Dawson elected to Hall of Fame |publisher=Yahoo! Inc. |date=2010-01-06 |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/news;_ylt=AmRZDXu1nmYqJO2KUwcHBQI5nYcB?slug=ap-halloffame&prov=ap&type=lgns |access-date=2010-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105212428/http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/news |archive-date=2010-01-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HOF">Blum, Ronald, Mike Fitzpatrick and Adam Pemble. [https://archive.today/20130210014915/http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/news;_ylt=An9J4Tyfsh8PYm9CQZywqw8RvLYF?slug=ap-halloffame&prov=ap&type=lgns "With Dawson in Hall, Future Bright for Blyleven"] . Associated Press. January 7, 2010.</ref>
==職業生涯==
===蒙特婁博覽會===
1975年美國職棒大聯盟選秀，博覽會在第11輪250順位選進道森。他在隔年9月11日登上大聯盟。1977年，他整年的打擊率為2成82，並敲出19轟與21次盜壘成功。最後他拿下國聯新人王。<ref name="HOF"/>道森是一名速度與力量兼具的球員，他在博覽會隊有7次達成單季20轟，而且生涯前7個球季皆能穩定送出至少20次盜壘成功。1980年，他拿下了生涯首座金手套獎。而且他也在1981年和1983年的MVP票選上拿下第二名。

在博覽會隊時期，道森一度豎下許多隊史單季紀錄。像是單季全壘打數、打點數、長打數與犧牲打數，其中犧牲打數至今仍是第一。而且他分別在1978年和1985年締造單局敲出兩轟的紀錄，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ATL/ATL197807300.shtml |title=July 30, 1978 Montreal Expos at Atlanta Braves Play by Play and Box Score |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |date=1978-07-30 |access-date=2012-08-01 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930165622/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ATL/ATL197807300.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHN/CHN198509240.shtml |title=September 24, 1985 Montreal Expos at Chicago Cubs Box Score and Play by Play |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |date=1985-09-24 |access-date=2012-08-01 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022009/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHN/CHN198509240.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>這項紀錄目前大聯盟歷史上僅有5名選手可達成。
===芝加哥小熊===
1986年球季結束後，道森成為自由球員。而他的膝蓋也深受人工草皮所苦，因此他希望自己可以到一個主場外野是自然草皮的球隊打球。<ref name="nyt6Jan2010">{{cite news|last=Kepner|first=Tyler|title=Following Long Wait, Dawson Enters Hall Alone|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/07/sports/baseball/07hall.html|access-date=20 July 2010|date=6 January 2010|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109043603/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/07/sports/baseball/07hall.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過道森因為與球隊老闆曾有過勾結紀錄，因此一度沒球隊要他。<ref name="NYTimes-Collusion">{{Cite news
  | last = Chass
  | first = Murray
  | author-link = Murray Chass
  | title = Big Collusion Winners: Clark, Parrish, Dawson
  | work = New York Times
  | date = 1992-12-15
  | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1992/12/15/sports/baseball-big-collusion-winners-clark-parrish-dawson.html
  | access-date = 2010-01-07
  | archive-date = 2018-01-16
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180116001947/http://www.nytimes.com/1992/12/15/sports/baseball-big-collusion-winners-clark-parrish-dawson.html
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>後來他跟小熊隊簽約，而他因為膝蓋傷勢移防中外野。當時他以50萬美元與球隊簽約，這是隊上球員第二低的紀錄。如果他在上半季沒有受傷的話可以得到15萬美元的額外獎金，入選明星賽可以再拿5萬美元。最後他兩項條件都達成了，小熊隊也再給他一個條件，如果他能拿下季後賽的系列賽MVP，他就能再拿到10萬美元加給。結果最後道森拿下年度MVP，小熊隊卻連季後賽都沒打進去，因此道森最終沒拿下那10萬元。<ref name="HOF"/><ref name="Tribune-GreenDawson">{{Cite news
  | last = Martinez
  | first = Michael
  | title = Dawson Named MVP
  | work = New York Times
  | date = 2010-01-07
  | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1987/11/19/sports/dawson-named-mvp.html
  | accessdate = 2021-01-13
  | archive-date = 2017-11-02
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171102020707/http://www.nytimes.com/1987/11/19/sports/dawson-named-mvp.html
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref><ref>Note that Bill James considers Dawson's best years to be from 1979 to 1983, with his higher Chicago numbers being due to [[Wrigley_Field|Wrigley Field]]'s advantageous environment for hitters (James 2001).</ref>

這年他敲出國聯最多的單季49轟，並拿下全壘打大賽冠軍。他也因此拿下年度MVP。不過小熊隊的戰績卻從季中的第一掉到最後一名，該年僅拿下76勝85敗，在東區排名墊底。<ref name="Baseball Reference.com ">{{cite web
