  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>後來他又在小熊待了5個球季。1989年，這年可說是道森打得最糟糕的一季，但是小熊卻闖進了季後賽。結果道森在國聯冠軍賽打擊率僅有1成05，小熊隊1勝4敗被巨人隊淘汰。
===生涯後期===
1992年球季結束後，道森成為自由球員。他在該年10月與紅襪隊簽約。<ref name="Tools">Edes, Gordon. [http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2006/01/10/dawson_had_the_tools_to_build_a_solid_case/?page=2 "Dawson Had the Tools to Build a Solid Case"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2006/01/10/dawson_had_the_tools_to_build_a_solid_case/?page=2 |date=20160303210309 }}. boston.com. January 10, 2006.</ref>1993年4月15日，他敲出生涯400轟。

他在紅襪隊待了兩年，因為膝傷所苦分別只出賽121場和75場比賽。之後他在馬林魚隊待了兩年，於1996年宣布退休。退休後，道森仍在馬林魚球團幕後工作。他也在2003年拿下他生涯第一枚冠軍戒。

2003年開始，他進入殯葬業服務。2020年4月，因為COVID-19疫情肆虐，意外導致道森的公司業績成長。不過他在受訪時仍提到這不是一件好事，他的妻子也因為這樣必須協助他處理更多工作事務。<ref name=Mortician>{{cite news |url=https://wgntv.com/news/coronavirus/you-see-a-lot-of-hurt-andre-dawson-deals-with-coronavirus-as-a-mortician/ |title='You see a lot of hurt': Andre Dawson deals with coronavirus as a mortician |agency=Associated Press |publisher=WGN-TV |date=April 30, 2020 |access-date=April 30, 2020 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021153427/https://wgntv.com/news/coronavirus/you-see-a-lot-of-hurt-andre-dawson-deals-with-coronavirus-as-a-mortician/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> At the time of the story, his wife of 42 years, Vanessa, was the office manager, while an uncle ran day-to-day operations.<ref name=Mortician/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2018/05/08/andre-dawson-hall-famer-funeral-home-florida-retirement/590358002/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-13 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803192705/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2018/05/08/andre-dawson-hall-famer-funeral-home-florida-retirement/590358002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.npr.org/2020/05/09/853216982/baseball-star-andre-dawson-on-running-a-funeral-home-during-the-pandemic |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-13 |archive-date=2020-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619183224/https://www.npr.org/2020/05/09/853216982/baseball-star-andre-dawson-on-running-a-funeral-home-during-the-pandemic |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===成就===
道森生涯敲出2774支安打、438轟、314次盜壘成功與1591分打點。歷史上只有8位球員能達成生涯300轟與300盜，而道森就是其中一人。他更是達成歷史上僅有5人達成的400轟300盜。

1997年，博覽會隊將道森的10號球衣永久退休(雖然這個號碼在1993年就因為Rusty Staub而退休一次了)。2010年，國民隊將他列入榮譽之戒的名單內。而他在2019年入選國家大學棒球名人堂。<ref>{{cite web |title=2019 College Baseball Hall of Fame Inductees |url=https://www.mlb.com/college-baseball-hall-of-fame/class-of-2019 |website=National College Baseball Hall of Fame |access-date=11 April 2020 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308143429/https://www.mlb.com/college-baseball-hall-of-fame/class-of-2019 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
